{"type": "article", "id": 11659, "title": "“Loop”灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-06T11:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021152448zjsbYHk9PnG4IiQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\">设计师 Constance Guisset 为意大利灯具公司 Fabbian 推出了一款名为 “Loop” 的灯具，它直径 45 厘米，使用喷砂吹制玻璃和喷漆金属制成。它看上去像是一个太空船，又像是少女的裙摆，也有点儿神似一个游来游去的水母。作为一款充满童趣的灯，它散发出的灯光柔和温暖，上部平坦可放置小玩具，下部线条流畅灵动，十分容易激发小孩子们的想像力。</span><a href=\"http://www.fabbian.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a><span style=\"text-align:justify;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135745ybBiaKljqroep7gQ.jpg\" width=\"765\" height=\"507\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6627451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135745yWJrG9a1oPFRmTYd.jpg\" width=\"765\" height=\"507\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6627451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135745SFea9ZcU1M38t7Vr.jpg\" width=\"765\" height=\"507\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6627451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135746IwYzM54yXWZQlVDf.jpg\" width=\"765\" height=\"507\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6627451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135746kISmzPbt2Q4LAaBf.jpg\" width=\"765\" height=\"507\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6627451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}